message.body: Liiiza. How's home? Sad I didn't get to see you again before you left, I was pulling some kind of crazy hours that week.

Nice good for you. What's the ego development task about? I'm good, almost moved to the center of dc but got cold feet bc it's $950/mo, though I may still hang out with the people living there. Set up a crazy expt at work today. You know, living the life.
